Ophir Energy May Seek to Raise Up to $400 Million in IPO, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-08T22:56:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/ophir-energy-may-seek-to-raise-up-to-400-million-in-ipo-ft-reports.html
Ophir Energy may raise up to $400
million in an initial public offering of its shares on the
London Stock Exchange, the Financial Times reported, without
attribution. The African explorer will announce tomorrow its
intention to list its shares on the London market, the FT said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 